title: FS: group of beater T200 Fatimas
author: bijoem

posts.post_title: FS: group of beater T200 Fatimas
posts.post_content:
asking $800 delivered insured for the group of seven T200s.
selling as a group only.

I started this a while back.  Tried to put the set together in beater quality so that I could put them in a frame and put it on the wall.

Maybe I can pass the baton on to someone else.

6 out of the 7 are obviously trimmed.
The Washington T200 was a PSA 2 that I cracked out.
